The **main pane** displays a table about \"Autonomous Triggering\" (自主触发), comparing current AI trigger conditions with future \"evolutionary behaviors.\"\n    *   A specific example at the bottom describes an AI perceiving that disk space is at 95%. Currently, it just says \"I feel bad,\" but the \"future evolution\" describes the AI analyzing the problem and proactively asking the user if it should clean the disk.\n\n### **Summary of the Desktop Layout**\n*   **Wallpaper:** Solid black.\n*   **Icons:** Located in a vertical left-side dock and as tabs within the browser. No icons are on the desktop itself.\n*   **Active Window:** A sophisticated AI-related tool called ClawX in a dark-themed UI."}],"details":{"model":"minimax-portal/MiniMax-VL-01","image":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\xiao-yi\\workspace\\perception_data\\desktop.png","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773837842632}}
