{"type":"message","id":"a3701151","parentId":"47aefa8e","timestamp":"2026-03-18T13:17:27.439Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在让我尝试生成一个有手绘感的壁纸 - 用水彩纹理效果。","thinkingSignature":"bf974c98f2b8a8f0cf56e3dc00aef6045c4068912c25d120ec463d8b50be3cf0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_owoip7bpj64u_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"Add-Type -AssemblyName System.Drawing\n\n$bmp = New-Object System.Drawing.Bitmap(1707, 960)\n$g = [System.Drawing.Graphics]::FromImage($bmp)\n\n# 水彩质感 - 柔和的渐变底色\n$brush = New-Object System.Drawing.Drawing2D.LinearGradientBrush(\n    (New-Object System.Drawing.Point(0, 0)),\n    (New-Object System.Drawing.Point(1707, 960)),\n    [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(255, 147, 112, 219),  # 矢车菊紫\n    [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(255, 255, 182, 193)   # 浅粉色\n)\n\n$g.FillRectangle($brush, 0, 0, 1707, 960)\n\n# 添加水彩纹理效果 - 多层半透明圆形\n$random = New-Object System.Random\n\n# 底层纹理 - 大面积柔和色块\nfor ($i = 0; $i -lt 20; $i++) {\n    $x = $random.Next(0, 1707)\n    $y = $random.Next(0, 960)\n    $w = $random.Next(200, 500)\n    $h = $random.Next(150, 400)\n    $alpha = $random.Next(20, 50)\n    $color = [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb($alpha, 255, 255, 255)\n    $brush2 = New-Object System.Drawing.SolidBrush($color)\n    $g.FillEllipse($brush2, $x, $y, $w, $h)\n}\n\n# 中层纹理 - 柔和的彩色光斑\n$colors = @(\n    [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(30, 255, 192, 203),\n    [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(30, 173, 216, 230),\n    [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(30, 221, 160, 246),\n    [System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb(30, 255, 218, 185)\n)\n\nfor ($i = 0; $i -lt 30; $i++) {\n    $x = $random.Next(0, 1707)\n    $y = $random.Next(0, 960)\n    $w = $random.Next(100, 300)\n    $h = $random.Next(80, 250)\n    $color = $colors[$random.Next(0, $colors.Count)]\n    $g.FillEllipse($color, $x, $y, $w, $h)\n}\n\n# 顶层 - 细腻的星光/光点\nfor ($i = 0; $i -lt 100; $i++) {\n    $x = $random.Next(0, 1707)\n    $y = $random.Next(0, 960)\n    $size = $random.Next(1, 2)\n    $alpha = $random.Next(100, 200)\n    $whiteBrush = New-Object System.Drawing.SolidBrush([System.Drawing.Color]::FromArgb($alpha, 255, 255, 255))\n    $g.FillEllipse($whiteBrush, $x, $y, $size, $size)\n}\n\n$bmp.Save(\"C:\\Users\\16343\\wallpaper_watercolor.bmp\")\n$g.Dispose()\n$bmp.Dispose()\n\nWrite-Host \"Watercolor hand-drawn style wallpaper created\"\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\xiao-yi\\workspace\\create_watercolor.ps1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":51872,"output":808,"cacheRead":37834,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90514,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773839828827}}
